<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="sapphire-heading-2">A Short Essay</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="sapphire-heading-2">Debunking the Myth</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="sapphire-heading-2">of the “Wu Xing Iris”</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="sapphire-heading-3">By Marquise-Cut ZIRCON Gabriel</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
